snippet.title: Terminal Error Demo | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Terminal Error is an experimental First-Person Point-and-Click horror game. Trapped in a nightmarish research facility, you must explore monster-infested hallways in the hopes of finding a way out.

Visit Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2502430/Terminal_Error/
Support on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/endspace/terminal-error

---
